page.title: 15YOUNG PEOPLE
page.content: {YOUNG PEOPLE} Young people around here are much the same as anywhere else in Britain today.They also like pop records,discos and motor bikes.They also like sports and football.In other words they like getting out and about. Because ours is a country place with very poor transport service. Young people have to have transport to get around.We spoke to some young people and they moaned a bit about how boring it is around here and one girl thought that people were very nosy,but most of them thought life around here was fine and that they'd really not like to live any where else.
